10. Conclusion

The central finding of this dossier is unambiguous: the commercially credible, culturally legible, and technologically compelling AI hardware category was never subtle. It was a console. It was always a console. Specifically, it was a console with Game Pass integration, AI modding, a creator marketplace, and enough legal ambiguity to feel alive.

